<p>
<h1>Add permissions for a resource to a user role</h1> 
</p>

<p><b>API Platform Base Path:</b> <code>https://api.enterprise.apigee.com/v1/o/{org_name}</code></p>

<div class="row">
	<div class="span6" style="width:340px;">

		<p><b>API Resource Path:</b> <code>/userroles/{role_name}/permissions</code></p>
		<p><b>Description:</b> Associates permissions for a resource with a user role
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="span6" style="width:340px;">
<table>		
	<tbody><tr><td><b>Verb:</b></td> <td><span class="verb-POST">POST</span></td></tr>
	<tr><td><b>Auth:</b></td> <td>Basic Auth</td></tr>


		<tr><td style="vertical-align:top"><b>Media types:</b></td>  <td>
<div class="content_type" id="content_type_1">
application/json
</div>
<div class="content_type" id="content_type_2">
text/xml
</div></td></tr>

		</tbody>
</table>


	</div>
</div>

<div class="span18">
	
		
	

	<b>Sample Request:</b>
	<pre class="terminal">$ curl  -X POST -d \
'{
	"path" : "/reports",
	"permissions" : [ "put", "get" ]
  }' \
https://api.enterprise.apigee.com/v1/o/{org_name}/userroles/{role_name}/permissions \
-u myname:mypass</div>


<b>Sample Response:</b> 
	<pre>{
	"path" : "/reports",
	"permissions" : [ "put", "get" ]
  }</pre>


	
</div>
